@defun fold kons knil clist1 clist2 @dots{}
@c EN
[SRFI-1] The fundamental list iterator.
When it is given a single list
@var{clist1} = (@var{e1} @var{e2} @dots{} @var{en}),
then this procedure returns
@c JP
